        <div class="msgSubject">FFXIV &quot;Flame Wars / Complaints&quot; Board Index Request</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-07 13:30:04   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-12891582041955293" id="quote-12891582041955293" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-12891582041955293" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=3&amp;mid=12891582041955293&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=12891582041955293&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_12891582041955293" onclick="followToggle('add','12891582041955293')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
